HOW TO BUILD
==================

The segatex-ng uses autoconf and automake for building.

$ aclocal
$ auconf
$ automake --add-missing

It is a good idea to first go through the options of configure by running:

$ ./configure --help

So, easy as this.

$ ./configure [options]
$ make

INSTALLATION
============

# make install

HOW TO USE 
==================

segatex-ng

CONFIGURATION
=============

No configuration.

